gnome-power-manager: gnome-power-manager (GNOME Power Manager)
gnome-power-manager: 
gnome-power-manager: GNOME Power Manager is a session daemon for the GNOME 
gnome-power-manager: Desktop environment that makes it easy to manage your laptop 
gnome-power-manager: or desktop system's power usage.  It requires HAL, and supports
gnome-power-manager: suspending, hibernating, power notifications, cpu frequencies, 
gnome-power-manager: hard drive spin-down, and display dimming. 
